pron. 自己；强调句中的男性主语或宾语
网络. 他自己；他亲自；他本人

自己；强调句中的男性主语或宾语

他自己；（用作男性的反身代词）自己；他亲自；他本人；用以强调男性主语或宾语；用于指代男性说话者或听话者认为重要的人物；用于指代先前提到的男性；用作反身代词强调动作的执行者；用于强调某男性是所做行为的责任人

1.en: Moon said to himself: "The children go for a hiking tomorrow, have to consult with the sun grandfather, make a good weather tomorrow. "
1.cn: 月亮自言自语地说：“明天孩子们去郊游，得去跟太阳公公商量商量，让明天有个好天气。”

2.en: The reason he gave for not cursing refusing himself was that there were was no financial game gain for him in making his decision.
2.cn: 他给出不回避的原因是没有任何金钱上的利益对他来说在他做出判决的时候。

3.en: And when drunk he cursed himself for allowing the state to see him as a symbol of continuity between the Russian and Soviet intelligentsia.
3.cn: 在喝酒的时候，他会诅咒自己让政府看到自己作为俄罗斯和苏维埃知识分子延续下的一种标志。

0.en: He has grown all these vegetables himself!
0.cn: 他自己种了所有这些蔬菜！

1.en: He picked it out of the toy store himself, he loves it.
1.cn: 他自己在玩具店选的，他很喜欢呢。

2.en: This is Grandpa Pig's vegetable garden. He has grown all these vegetables himself!
2.cn: 这是猪爷爷的蔬菜园。他自己种了所有这些蔬菜！

3.en: This is Grandpa Pig's vegetable garden. He has grown all these vegetables himself!
3.cn: 这是猪爷爷的蔬菜园。他自己种了所有这些蔬菜！

4.en: Slain by the jabberwocky, on horunvendush day, many years ago. He's just not himself anymore.
4.cn: 女王决战日那天，他全家被加勃沃奇杀害了。已经过去很多年了，疯帽子也不是他自己了。

5.en: Nonsense. He can fight his own battles. Colonel, he was obviously being bullied and he defended himself.
5.cn: 胡说，他能打赢他自己的战斗，上校，很显然他被欺负了，他只是在正当防卫，孩子。

6.en: So he gives himself the idea. Precisely. That's the only way it will stick. It has to seem self-generated.
6.cn: 总言之他自己为自己植入意念。没错，让他自然而然有此意念。

7.en: That is the same Peeta that defended you at the whipping post. No, it's not. Now he's only defending himself.
7.cn: 是他保护你不受人鞭打。不，不是，现在他只是保护着他自己。

8.en: I'm sorry. He's asked me to hold all calls, unless you're Stephen Hawking, his mother or himself from the future.
8.cn: 抱歉，他让我过滤所有电话，除非打来的人是斯蒂芬·霍金，他妈妈或是来自未来的他自己。

9.en: It wasn't even an official sign-up sheet. He printed it himself, and he put his name down on every slot for the next six months.
9.cn: 那甚至都不是正式的登记表格，他自己打印出来在每一个机位都写上自己的名字，使用六个月。

10.en: This guy sits here on his butt, all alone, clearly doesn't leave the house. He talks a good game, but he doesn't care about anyone but himself.
10.cn: 这家伙一天到晚宅在家里，大门不出二门不迈的，他吹得天花乱坠，其实他心里就只关心他自己。

11.en: Snape doesn't want the Stone for himself. He wants the Stone for Voldemort. With the Elixir of Life, Voldemort will be strong again. He'll come back.
11.cn: 斯内普不是为了他自己，他偷石头是为了伏地魔，有长生不老药给伏地魔恢复元气，让他卷土重来。

12.en: So? So why is it no longer a specialty? Did the chef lose confidence in the dish or himself? And look over here. Shrimp in mobster sauce. What is mobster sauce?
12.cn: 所以呢？所以它为什么不是招牌菜了呢？这里的厨师是对这道菜没了信心，还是对他自己没了信心啊？再看这里，强盗酱沾鲜虾，强盗酱是什么？

13.en: And earlier this month the president of Kentucky State University set a great example by giving himself a $90,000 pay cut so that he could give raises to his lowest-paid employees.
13.cn: 本月初，肯塔基州立大学的校长为大家树立了榜样，他自己减薪9万美元，用这些钱为低收入员工提高工资。

14.en: When I really looked at everything, everything a basketball player Could do for himself individually And for a team, Jeremy Lin was the best player here, But yet colleges weren't clamoring for him. He just didn't fit the mold.
14.cn: 当我纵观这一切，一个篮球运动员能够为他自己，为球队做的一切，林书豪都是这里最好的球员，可是大学并没有争着要他，他不符合固有的模式

15.cn: 到底是谁只会关心自己？

16.cn: 他把自己拉起来了，站立的人。

17.en: They'd say, "Why does he touch himself so much?"
17.cn: 那这些墙会说"为何他这么喜欢自摸"？

18.en: And he would be better advised to go fuck himself.

19.en: Butterfly could've gotten himself home from Arizona.
19.cn: 蝴蝶可以自己从亚利桑那州飞回家。
